  "stem": "<p>The function <i>p</i> is defined by <i>p</i>(<i>x</i>) = 6<i>x</i> + <i>a</i>, where <i>a</i> is a constant. If <i>p</i>(3) = 20, what is the value of <i>a</i>?</p>",
